KMFDMMoney048A.name: KMFDM BRUTE Money a #048
description: Introducing the first of my many self portraits on KMFDM covers
(I modelled for the shotgun-toting, drug-dealing pimp character)
Money unflinchingly encapsulates the urban consequences of
capitalism (prostitution, drugs and violence). Fans have asked
me over the years what is in the wrapper in his open hand.
Originally, it was supposed to be a wrap of heroin or coke but
dealers no longer use that method of packaging. I've thought
of changing it to something more recognisable (a pill or
capsule), but I quite like the mystery that now surrounds the
object - BRUTE!"
